{
  "stem": "24231.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was-- that's how I really lived through the time in Prague with the German.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I lived in a-- in a town, which is-- which was called Prague 18.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Prague town was divided into sections.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like here in New York, we have Brooklyn, Queens, Manhattan.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had-- I was in Prague 18, which was called Stresovice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was an, an older section where I lived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was also a newer section.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Jewish section was mainly Prague 1, which was called Josefov.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's where the ghetto, the original ghetto, used to be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's presently is the, the-- the Jewish cemetery is there also, and the synagogues.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, our-- our-- my parents belonged to a synagogue, which was a modern synagogue.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was in Prague, in Smichov, which was-- and because my grandfather was Orthodox, it was closer to walk there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was only about like four miles instead of going, going like seven miles to Prague.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we, we belonged to that synagogue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That synagogue later on was used as a storage house during the Germans, and they put all kinds of things in it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I, I went there after the war and it just is standing there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's, It's no more a synagogue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's just-- I don't know what they converted it to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My, my, father only went through secondary school, which was about nine years of, of schooling, and then he had a trade school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "However, my mother was-- had a business school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so she was-- she was really keeping-- when my father had the business, so she was keeping the books for him and did all the arrangements.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He just ran the-- ran the business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We, we-- because when my grandfather was alive, I remember we were celebrating holidays.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
